description: Welcome to 22 Liberty Drive Premier Luxury waterfront residences.This stunning front facing corner residence features 2 bedrooms+Den,floor to ceiling windows with amazing water views,Gorgeous kitchen with center island,custom high-gloss white lacquer cabinetry,appliances Wolf stove & wall oven,Miele,Subzero,wine chiller.Spacious open floor concept living/dining room that leads to the private balcony over looking the City Skyline&Boston Harbor.The primary beautiful corner suite boasts panoramic amazing water views,luxurious bathroom with marble soaking tub,glass enclosed shower,double vanity,walk-in closet.2nd bedroom en-suite features water views,custom closet,fulll bath.Plus Den for great home office or guestroom. Direct acces to 1 car deeded parking, plus 2 storage units.Amenities include 24 hour concierge/doorman,fitness center,residents lounge with private waterfront terrace over looking the harbor walk.Located to Seaport District's finest restaurants,shops,cafes,shops,Airport

exclusions: Dining Room Chandelier And Den Shelving.
